iority and then start on hp/mana items.  Also I do not have Luclin but might be willing to get if really advantageous…haven’t even touched the surface of Velious so I am loath to line Verant’s pocket with another expansion I won’t head to.  [PS. I Love being bound in the Firepot room]<BR></font></td>
